				While I have not actually gotten to a level with which to use this spell (as an enchantress at least) I would like to comment about mana.  A NPC or monsters is far superior to lowly pathetic PC's, this is the way Verant designed the game.  It appears they have unlimited mana compared to the pathetic PC caster, who has much less mana.  A mob caster of equal level casts around 3 times as fast, is about 4 times less likely to be interrupted, channel rate seems about the same.<BR>
Also they have around 3 or 4 times as much mana.  Its not unlimited, its just very large.  This spell better drain a very large amount of mana to make it worth casting.
